      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
      "body" : "Good question. I had to look it up. See <a href=\"http://tutorials.jenkov.com/java-reflection/generics.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">tutorials.jenkov.com/java-reflection/generics.html</a> Note that getMethod just takes the class of the generic e.g. Set. So getMethod would want to two return methods for the submitters code, which it can&#39;t."
