      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
      "body" : "Then the getMethod method needs fixing. For example introduce an overload wich specifies generic overload and make the original method return non-generic version only, not returning any method anotated as generic. Of course this should have been done in version 1.5. If they do it now they will break backward compatibility of the method. I stand by my statement that type erasure does not dictate this behaviour. It is the implementation that did not get enough work probably due to limited resources."
