    "question_id" : 1998544,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I think it is because of type erasure since after compilation both the Integer and String will be replaced with Object hence resulting in two functions with the same parameters which is against method overloading</p>\n"
